---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /books/book-002/
title: Album of Memories, Book 2
---

<div class="index-page">
  <nav class="page-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/books/">Books</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
    <span aria-current="page">Book 2</span>
  </nav>

  <h1>Album of Memories — Book 2</h1>
  <p class="index-page__lede">
    The second volume continues the family record, with additional
    correspondence, photographs, and clippings.
  </p>

  <ul class="book-pages">
    {%- for page in collections.pagesByBook[2] -%}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ page.url }}">
          <img class="book-pages__thumb"
               src="/books/book-002/images/thumb/{{ page.data.image }}"
               alt=""
               loading="lazy" />
          <span class="book-pages__info">
            <span class="book-pages__num">P. {{ page.data.pageNumber }}</span>
            <span class="book-pages__title">{{ page.data.title }}</span>
            {%- if page.data.date_range -%}
              <span class="book-pages__meta">{{ page.data.date_range }}</span>
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
    {%- else -%}
      <li><em>No pages transcribed yet.</em></li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</div>
